item.title: EXPIRED 09/25
item.description: GRUNGY! Shot on OLYMPUS AF35 SUPER with expired film. Same as the film on the STELLENBOSCH 10/25 album except in that case I had pulled by 2 stops when developing. Cleaning Peppermencino (previously Vincenzo) in preparation for the proposal in 3 weeks time. Shoutout Steve for helping me transport him to Claremont. Isuzu outside of Majuba. Tennis courts. Lazy day with Su in HQ at Emma & Faffa.

item.title: STELLENBOSCH 10/25
item.description: Botmaskop with Luthando and Banda before 2L's surgery. Moved into Huis Willem, Leef Op Hoop on 1st of October - spot the double exposure. Springsteen at Labia with Suki, Steve and Bee. Chess with Alastair. Bougainvillea at Rotavi. Featuring Heath, Edward & CAT Machinery. Shot on Steve's Canon AE-1 (35mm lens) on expired film from 1980s that was going for R100 at Tothills. Pulled by 2 stops to overexpose as expired film loses light sensitivity.
